                "editor": "<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;\">By accessing our website or engaging Regal Plumbing &amp; Rooter for plumbing services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use our website or services.</p>"
