              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;\">Regal Plumbing &amp; Rooter provides residential and commercial plumbing services including emergency plumbing, drain cleaning, sewer line repair, water heater installation and repair, slab leak detection, hydrojetting, gas leak detection, and water filtration system installation. CA Contractor License #1097482.</p>"
