              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;\">A service agreement is established when you contact us and we agree to perform work, you accept an estimate from our technicians, or work begins with your consent. We reserve the right to refuse service at our discretion.</p>"
