              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style=\"font-size:15px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;\"><strong>Labor Warranty:</strong> All labor is warranted against defects for 30 days from service date.<br><strong>Parts Warranty:</strong> Parts and materials are covered by manufacturer warranty.<br><strong>Drain Cleaning:</strong> 30-day warranty against the same blockage returning, provided no foreign objects are introduced. Warranties are void if the system is modified by another party after our work.</p>"
